keyFacts: The document is an FBI form created to document victim outreach support efforts for the Jeffrey Epstein child sex trafficking case.
The efforts were specifically related to a November 11, 2020 briefing by the Office of the Deputy Attorney General (ODAG) on Case Progress Review (CPR) findings.
The document includes an enclosure with updated contact information as of November 18, 2020.
The FBI case ID number for the Epstein investigation is 50D-NY-3027571.
